<%= render "include/navbar" %>

<div class="jumbotron about-header">
	<h1 class="no-logo vision">Helping Muslim gets halalan thayyiban around the world.</h1>
	<h2>That is our simple vision.</h2>
</div>

<div class="container-fluid about-content">
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12">
			<h2>About Us</h2>
			<p>HalalData.org is a community search engine for muslim traveler to get information about halal place around the world.</p>
			<p>It is an initiative from <a href="http://asep.co" target="_blank">Asep.co</a>; an app studio from Indonesia.</p>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="row manifesto">
		<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-sm-offset-1 col-md-8 col-md-offset-1">
			<h2>Manifesto</h2>
			<ol>
				<li>By mentioning halal data, we mean any foods and beverages that safe to be consumed by muslim; e.g., certified halal food/beverage, vegetarian food/beverage, or any place that provide halal food.</li>
				<li>HalalData.org is a non profit initiative and we always open for contribution from everyone to make HalalData better.</li>
				<li>All data in our database are opened for everyone to download and use for any halal purposes either commercial or not.<span style="color: red;">*</span></li>
			</ol>
			<p><span style="color: red;">*</span> This feature will be developed soon.</p>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="row manifesto">
		<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-sm-offset-1 col-md-8 col-md-offset-1">
			<h2>How to Contribute</h2>
			<ol>
				<li>If you want to help us by providing halal data in your city or country, you can <%= link_to "sign up", new_user_registration_path %> and start creating the data.</li>
				<li>If you have a desire to be a data validator for your city you can talk to us at <%= link_to "halaldata@asep.co", "mailto: halaldata@asep.co" %>.</li>
				<li>Do you code in Ruby and want to help us improve HalalData.org platform? Great, let's talk also at <%= link_to "halaldata@asep.co", "mailto: halaldata@asep.co" %>. Honestly we don't have a lot of developers, so your codes are welcome.</li>
				<li>
					If you don't have any time to contribute using your energy, maybe you can contribute by donating. A little fund from you will be very helpful for HalalData.org operation. <br>
					<form action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post" target="_top">
					<input type="hidden" name="cmd" value="_s-xclick">
					<input type="hidden" name="hosted_button_id" value="3EBQYDZPQN5L2">
					<input type="image" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_donateCC_LG.gif" border="0" name="submit" alt="PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!">
					<img alt="" border="0" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif" width="1" height="1">
					</form>

				</li>
				<li>Don't have anything to contribute? No problem. Just tell about HalalData.org to your friends and family members. Help them to avoid consume non-halal food and beverage.</li>
			</ol>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>